{% include 'layouts/partials/header.njk' %}

<section id="intro">
    <div class="grid col-auto sm:grid-cols-2 mb-2">

        <div class="sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <p>
                <span class="text-lg font-sans font-semibold">Hi, I'm Ed Marsh</span>. I'm a <a href="/skills/technical-writing">technical communicator</a>, <a href="/skills/content-strategy">content strategist</a>, <a href="/podcasts">podcaster</a>, and <a href="/skills/community">community builder</a>. I'm passionate about creating and managing content that's clear, concise, and consistent. I specialize in building or revamping documentation practices.</p>

            <p class="mt-6">My job title has always been technical writer, but I've made complex information accessible for over three decades by incorporating information architecture, content strategy, and community.<p>

                    <p class="mt-6">This site is my portfolio. I rebuilt it from the ground up in WordPress to the <a href="https://eleventy.dev">Eleventy static site generator</a> to show how I can help organizations with all aspects of their content.</p>
                    <p class="mt-6">My process involves:</p>

                    <ul class="list-inside">
                        <li>Assessing your current content situation.</li>
                        <li>Defining structure.</li>
                        <li>Implementing content strategy.</li>
                        <li>Engaging the people in your organization who are documentation advocates.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 rounded-lg max-w-48">
                    <img
        src="/assets/images/ed-marsh.jpg"
        alt="Ed Marsh, photo courtesy Arclight Images"
        title="Ed Marsh, photo courtesy Arclight Images"
      >
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="grid-border" style="border: 3px solid var(--medium-blue); border-radius: 1rem; padding:6px;">
        {% set collectionName = "skills" %}
        <section class="mx-auto" id="{{collectionName}}">
            <h2 class="px-3">How I can help you</h2>
            <p class="description px-3 text-jet-100">Here are the biggest ways I can help your organization. <a href="/skills/">See all the ways I can help</a>.</p>
            <div class="grid col-auto sm:grid-cols-4 gap-2 px-3">

                {% set featured = collections[collectionName] | filterBy("data.featured", true) %}
                {% set sortedFeatured = featured | sort(false, false, "data.featuredOrder") %}
                {% for item in sortedFeatured %}
                    {% if loop.index0 < 4 %}
                        {% include 'layouts/partials/card.njk' %}
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
            </div>

        </section>
        {% set collectionName = "ssg" %}
        <section class="mx-auto mt-10" id="{{collectionName}}" style="border-top: 2px solid var(--bg-jet-100);">
            <h2 class="px-3">Creating a static site</h2>
            <p class="description px-3 text-jet-100">I updated and simplified my old WordPress site using the <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/">Eleventy static site generator</a>. Here's how I can use the lessons learned to help you meet your content goals. <span class="col-span-full text-lg font-bold italic">
                    <a href="/static-site-transformation/">Check back frequently to read the full series!</a></span></p>

            <div class="grid col-auto sm:grid-cols-4 gap-2 px-3">

                {% set featured = collections[collectionName] | filterBy("data.featured", true) %}
                {% set sortedFeatured = featured | sort(false, false, "data.featuredOrder") %}
                {% for item in sortedFeatured %}
                    {% if loop.index0 < 4 %}
                        {% include 'layouts/partials/card.njk' %}
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </section>

       {% set collectionName = "podcasts" %}
       <section class="mx-auto mt-10" id="{{collectionName}}" style="border-top: 2px solid var(--bg-jet-100); ">
            <h2 class="px-3">Recent podcasts</h2>
            <p class="description px-3 text-jet-100">I created (and played every role for) the <a href="podcasts/">Content Content podcast</a>, where I interviewed "the people behind the content" in technical communication, content strategy, content marketing, implementation, and more.
   Check out <span class="text-lg italic">
                    <a href="/podcasts/">all of the amazing people I spoke with.</a>
                </span>
            </p>
            <div class="grid col-auto sm:grid-cols-4 gap-2 px-3">

                {% for item in collections.podcasts | reverse %}
                    {% if loop.index0 <= 3 %}
                        {% include 'layouts/partials/card.njk' %}
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}

            </div>
        </section>
    </section>
    {% include 'layouts/partials/footer.njk' %}